If you want something more concrete than “just draw” I’d recommend timed drawings. Start with a really short time and slowly build up. Swapping between drawing the whole thing roughly and drawing a smaller part more carefully is something you should do from time to time. Loosening up is also important. Quickposes is good for timed drawing. If you want to start where I did I’d start with 30 second head drawings before changing it up whenever you feel comfortable doing so.
